front.title: Awwww, Cannot Get Your Ship Out
front.gametext: Deploy on a landed starship (not at a docking bay). Starship may not move. OR Deploy on a starship or vehicle on Dagobah. Starship or vehicle may not move. At the start of you next control phase, starship or vehicle 'sinks' to the Used Pile.
front.lore: 'Listen, friend, we didn't mean to land in that puddle, and if we could get our ship out, we would, but we can't so why don't you just...'
